   "source": [
    "# 🎵 Herry Music Transcription - Google Colab Quick Test\n",
    "\n",
    "Convert PDF sheet music to MuseScore format using advanced image recognition!\n",
    "\n",
    "**Features:**\n",
    "- 📄 Extract images from PDF files\n",
    "- 🎼 Detect musical staff lines\n",
    "- 🎹 Recognize note positions\n",
    "- 🎵 Estimate pitch values\n",
    "- 📊 Generate MusicXML for MuseScore\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "install_dependencies"
   },
   "source": [
    "## Step 1: Install System & Python Dependencies\n",
    "\n",
    "This installs all required packages for PDF processing and music notation."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "install_system_deps"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Install system dependencies\n",
    "!apt-get update -qq\n",
    "!apt-get install -y poppler-utils python3-dev > /dev/null 2>&1\n",
    "print(\"✅ System dependencies installed\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "install_python_deps"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Install Python dependencies\n",
    "import subprocess\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "\n",
    "dependencies = [\n",
    "    'pdf2image>=1.16.3',\n",
    "    'opencv-python>=4.8.0',\n",
    "    'music21>=8.3.0',\n",
    "    'numpy>=1.24.0',\n",
    "    'Pillow>=10.0.0'\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "for dep in dependencies:\n",
    "    subprocess.check_call([sys.executable, \"-m\", \"pip\", \"install\", \"-q\", dep])\n",
    "    print(f\"✅ Installed {dep.split('>')[0]}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n🎉 All dependencies installed successfully!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "download_music_transcriber"
   },
   "source": [
    "## Step 2: Download the Music Transcriber Module\n",
    "\n",
    "Fetch the music_transcriber.py from GitHub repository."
