   "source": [
    "## 🔧 Troubleshooting\n",
    "\n",
    "### Issue: No notes detected\n",
    "```\n",
    "Solutions:\n",
    "1. Ensure PDF is scanned at 300+ DPI\n",
    "2. Check that staff lines are clear and visible\n",
    "3. Use printed sheet music (not handwritten)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Issue: \"Cannot find a usable mro_class_name\"\n",
    "```\n",
    "Solution: This is fixed - we installed poppler-utils\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Issue: \"ModuleNotFoundError\"\n",
    "```\n",
    "Solution: Re-run the dependency installation cell\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Issue: File too large\n",
    "```\n",
    "Solution: Maximum 50MB - compress your PDF first\n",
    "```\n",
